CASE ANNOUNCEMENTS

September 22, 2008

[Cite as 09/22/2008 Case Announcements, 2008-0hio-4761.]

DISCIPLINARY CASES

2008-1708. Cleveland Metro. Bar Assn. v. Polke.

Upon consideration of the motion for admission pro hac vice of Theodore A. Barone by Gaetano Barone,

It is ordered by the court that the motion for admission pro hac vice is granted.
